      <li>3–5 minutes: partner discussion</li>
      <li>As students work, decide which categories will go in the question stems for the next problem.</li>
      <li><p>Consider providing these sentence stems if students need support explaining their reasoning:</p><ul>
<li>
<q>Yo supe que la afirmación era falsa porque . . .</q></li>
